1997;;Under the Lighthouse Dancing;;Australian;;Graeme Rattigan;;Jack Thompson, Jacqueline McKenzie, Naomi Watts;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Under_the_Lighthouse_Dancing;;Three couples travel to Rottnest Island near Perth, Western Australia for the weekend. One of the couples announces that they intend to get married and when the bride-to-be tells the others that she is terminally ill, they make sure the wedding takes place that weekend.